_sText:
A simple remake of the famous map "3mc\_training".


ADDED:

- More detail and realism;
- New spots and rooms;
- Sun environment;
- New Skybox;
- 3D Skybox;
- Dynamic lights with physics (ragdoll if you shoot or touch them) in the indoors;
- Player clips to fix some bad/unfair camping spots, and now the palms are real! You can't pass through them;
- More tactics available for Terrorists adding a scalable rope on the right of the T spawn to reach immediately the second floor;
- More tactics available for Counter-Terrorists adding an indoor stairway on the left of the CT spawn to reach the second floor paying less attention to the Terrorists shots;
- Forced lightmap at 3 on the outdoor floor to make the shadows looks much better;
- Lighting atmosphere is now realistic.

You may have some FPS decrease by 30/40 because of the modify, if you want to play with good FPS (if you have a bad computer), try to turn the shadows "Min." in the advanced video options.


INSTALL:

Put the "3mc\_training\_detailed.bsp" file into your "counter-strike source/cstrike/maps" directory, and then run the game by clicking "Create Server" and selecting "3mc\_training\_detailed".
